channel.title: Important Dates In The Auxy Community?
channel.description:
I'm wondering about some important dates in the Auxy community:
When did the iPad app originally release? When did you update the iPad app to the new logo? When did you originally release Auxy for iPhone (with the iPad app-like interface)? When did you update Auxy to the interface we all know and love today?
Those are just some questions I've been wondering about. Thanks for your time! NYC
